{"tid":393792,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會唔想生仔？而去收養？","createTime":"2017-09-09T13:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T13:46:49.000Z","uid":14392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff38ba95a7ab0d2257e4709e4a66e56c8a18e80","tid":393792,"uid":14392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a647c0664b15bf1a000cf6bb7c0966f2db2fac2c","tid":393792,"uid":140112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:46:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以呢？人地生定唔生同領養係冇衝突，加上人地領養係人地既自由。<br />\n再者，人地背後可以係怕痛、怕懷孕麻煩、怕基因不良等，你點知人諗咩？<br />\n加上，人地既出發點同心態都係幫人，又合乎道德，值得支持。<br />\nBtw, 母產子同人工受孕夠唔合乎自然，個重點其實係薪火相傳，智慧可以傳承，人類繼續繁衍，生生不息，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">防止滅絕</span>就足夠啦！"}]}